{
  "stem": "20084.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember the hours when it was, but it was maybe once a week or so for.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then in the after school-- I think the school was till 1 or 2 o'clock-- then we went to Hebrew school in the afternoon on our own.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we played soccer, but not-- not personal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't want to be friends with us, and the same thing was our parents didn't care that we'd be friends with them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a mixed bag, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- I was good with my hands.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very mechanically inclined.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was fixing things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was doing-- I was building crystal sets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I enjoyed that type of work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was always fixing something for the neighbor, always manage something to get a few pennies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Pennies were [POLISH], called in Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, I always had for a few.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't get any spending money or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no toy store that you went out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You make your own toys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And your biggest toy was a old carriage with four wheels if you could manage get it from some yard somewhere, buy it or something and riding down the hill, or creating your own toys, whatever you could make with your hands, put together.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was the toys that was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But life, life wasn't bad, wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Was very disciplined.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "School was very disciplined.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The teachers were-- some of the teachers-- one in particular teacher was very sadistic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if you didn't obey something, he'd call you in front of him and you had to raise your hand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he used to take you-- that hand is too high.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now it's too high.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's too high.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Lower it down a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Lower it down a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
